  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要做一个用户旅程图，聚焦在\"添加商品到愿望清单\"这个核心场景。用户从进入在线商店开始，一直到成功把商品加入愿望清单为止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Adding an item to the wishlist",
        "Enter online shop",
        "Browse online shop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，这个旅程分成两大阶段对吧？先处理\"进入在线商店\"的部分，然后是\"浏览商店\"。我想确认一下，登录环节你们用的是Education_LMS_Portal这个系统吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Enter online shop",
        "Log in (Education_LMS_Portal)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Education_LMS_Portal是我们的统一认证入口。用户满意度方面，访问网站和浏览首页都是5分，但登录只有3分，因为偶尔会有认证延迟的问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visit website",
        "Log in (Education_LMS_Portal)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，第一部分完成了。现在进入\"浏览在线商店\"阶段——这里步骤比较多，我梳理一下：用户先滚动首页、查看分类、进入具体分类、应用筛选条件，然后浏览商品列表，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scroll through start page",
        "Check out categories",
        "Go to category",
        "Apply filter to category",
        "Scroll through products"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，但后面还有关键几步：用户进入商品详情页后，通常会先看评论——这里有个有趣的数据，第一条评论满意度只有1分，因为用户觉得不够有参考价值，但再看一条就变成5分了。然后检查商品变体，最后点击\"Add to wishlist\"按钮并选择具体的愿望清单。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go to product",
        "Read review",
        "Read another review",
        "Check out product variants",
        "Click on \"Add to wishlist\"",
        "Choose wishlist"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "收到。我注意到\"Add to wishlist\"和\"Choose wishlist\"都是5分，说明这个核心功能体验很好。不过\"Read review\"和\"Read another review\"是同一个动作重复两次吗？需要区分清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Read review",
        "Read another review",
        "Click on \"Add to wishlist\"",
        "Choose wishlist"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这是两次独立的阅读行为，用户会连续看两条评论。第一条失望，第二条满意，所以分数不同。另外\"Check out product variants\"是3分，因为变体选择界面还有点复杂。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Read review",
        "Read another review",
        "Check out product variants"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部确认了。旅程图已完整呈现：从访问网站、Education_LMS_Portal登录，到首页浏览、分类筛选、商品详情页的两轮评论阅读、变体检查，最终通过\"Add to wishlist\"完成添加。所有满意度评分都已标注。",
